</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 13px;"><i>Chief Executive Officer of Brookfield Renewable Group</i></span></font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
